Package: GForecast
Type: Package
Title: Fit ARIMA or ETS model to grouped time series data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: James Craig
Maintainer: James Craig <jamescraig39@gmail.com>
Description: A method for fitting an ARIMA or ETS model on time series data with a group identifier.  gForecast first nests each group in it's own data.tbl, fits and forecasts new values based on specified model, then returns a single logitudinal data frame with forecasted values appended to orginal data.
Depends: R (>= 2.1.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    forecast,
    tidyquant,
    timetk,
    sweep,
    purrr,
    zoo,
    lubridate
Suggests: 
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
